      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Weak maiden where EL RENO (5) can feature. Tested to a mile last time in and looks well placed here fresh. Fitter for two jump-outs and should be primed for a big return. Has shown enough to claim this. ENTITLE (6) is a well-travelled mare fitter for two runs back for the new yard. Extra trip suits and best figures stack up. Won't get a better chance to find some form. FLYING NIC (7) looks suited by the extra trip and will be winding up late. Same goes for HAVILAH (8) who turned in a better run last time to place. Watch the market closely with the first starter FINAL COMMAND (1). First-starter by Fleet Review out of Mintenko. Well educated and coming along nicely leading into this, most recently winning a Moe jump-out. Wouldn't have to be a star.",
